
File for the ntnuthesis LaTeX class.
This class produces a subset of book suitable for 
theses written at NTNU.

Original author: Federico Zenith

Edit: Arne Tobias Elve (tobelve@gmail.com) 2015

options:

a4crop  - Produces A4 size paper with b5 size text zoomed into a corner
a4paper - Produces A4 paper. Use for project.
10pt    - fontsize
11pt    - fontsize (default)
12pt    - fontsize
screen  - Produces screensize pdf
draft   - Use this option if frontpage is to be included.
final   - Produces b5 pdf used for delivering the final report.
          This option removes the front page if \mktitle is used
          for producing the front page




